videos.description: Anthony Davis comes out hot with two dunks, a sweet layup and a block on Nikola Jokic.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (AD impresses early with a couple dunks and a block on Jokic) 2022/04/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: AD impresses early with a couple dunks and a block on Jokic

videos.description: Anthony Davis goes at Nikola Jokic and Eurosteps before flipping in the shot plus the foul.

videos.headline: AD Euros into impressive and-1

videos.description: Anthony Davis denies the shot at the rim, leading to a Lakers fast break that ends in a Talen Horton-Tucker and-1.

videos.description: Anthony Davis goes behind his back before finishing the layup plus the foul.

videos.description: Bones Hyland gets out in transition and finishes the sweet layup.

videos.description: Nikola Jokic goes for 38 points, grabs 18 rebounds and dishes out 6 assists, leading the Nuggets to a victory in LA over the Lakers.
